            "title": "鴻海5月營收6157億元創同期高 消費智能繳月增力抗匯率波動",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>鴻海 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2317:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2317\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2317-TW</a>) 今 (5) 日公告 5 月營收 6157.45 億元，雖月減近 4%，但年增 11.92%，創同期新高，其中消費智能產品繳出月增表現；累計前 5 月營收近 2.9 兆元，年增 21.65%，也是歷年同期最佳。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008537%2Fl%2Fbc2e96b9eed6a1071cc8da9d3690de59.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008537%2Fl%2Fbc2e96b9eed6a1071cc8da9d3690de59.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008537%2Fl%2Fbc2e96b9eed6a1071cc8da9d3690de59.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008537%2Fl%2Fbc2e96b9eed6a1071cc8da9d3690de59.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008537%2Fl%2Fbc2e96b9eed6a1071cc8da9d3690de59.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008537%2Fl%2Fbc2e96b9eed6a1071cc8da9d3690de59.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008537%2Fl%2Fbc2e96b9eed6a1071cc8da9d3690de59.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008537%2Fl%2Fbc2e96b9eed6a1071cc8da9d3690de59.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008537%2Fl%2Fbc2e96b9eed6a1071cc8da9d3690de59.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008537%2Fl%2Fbc2e96b9eed6a1071cc8da9d3690de59.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008537%2Fl%2Fbc2e96b9eed6a1071cc8da9d3690de59.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008537%2Fl%2Fbc2e96b9eed6a1071cc8da9d3690de59.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008537%2Fl%2Fbc2e96b9eed6a1071cc8da9d3690de59.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008537%2Fl%2Fbc2e96b9eed6a1071cc8da9d3690de59.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008537%2Fl%2Fbc2e96b9eed6a1071cc8da9d3690de59.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008537%2Fl%2Fbc2e96b9eed6a1071cc8da9d3690de59.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008537%2Fl%2Fbc2e96b9eed6a1071cc8da9d3690de59.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">鴻海5月營收6157億元創同期高 消費智能產品抗匯率波動逆勢月增。(鉅亨網資料照)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>鴻海說明，5 月四大產品類別表現來看，雖受有匯率影響，但消費智能產品拉貨動能強勁，營收仍較上月成長；雲端網路、電腦終端產品則較約略衰退；元件及其他產品也呈現衰退。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>若與去年同期相比，雲端網路產品強勁成長、元件及其他產品顯著成長、消費智能產品約略持平，僅電腦終端產品拉貨動能放緩、呈現年減；前 5 月來看，雲端網路、元件及其他、電腦終端等產品均強勁成長，消費智能產品則持平。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>展望第二季，鴻海重申，仍屬傳統淡季，主要產品進入新舊產品轉換期，但雲端網路產品將保持成長趨勢，以目前能見度來看，預估第二季無論季對季、年對年都有顯著成長，但仍需持續關注全球政經局勢及匯率變化之影響。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
